; Regression test for issue #958: Fixated prices vanish when commodity
; equivalencies exist.
;
; When a commodity equivalency (C directive) exists for a commodity,
; lot annotations (fixated prices, lot prices, lot notes) must be
; preserved through reduce/unreduce conversions.

C 1 widget = 2 thingy

2013/05/07 Widgits-R-Us
    Assets:Widgets         1 widget {=$10}
    Income:Gifts           $-10

; Fixated lot price must survive C directive in --lots output
test bal --lots Assets:Widgets
     1 widget {=$10}  Assets:Widgets
end test

; Per-unit cost must survive C directive in --lots output
test bal --lot-prices Assets:Widgets
     1 widget {=$10}  Assets:Widgets
end test
